{
  "stem": "3666.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I happen to have married a man from that region of Europe, and he told me later that the Jews in Hungary or Czechoslovakia did look down at Polish Jews.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know why.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's silly, but it did happen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The tragedy was that they were all killed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The whole transport.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was-- that was in Riga, maybe not late 1944, maybe middle of 1944.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, some time in 1944 when we were in Riga-- actually, from Riga, we were taken to Stutthof.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was a [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the worst.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the worst.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Those were horrible moments.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Again, we were given numbers, not on my hand.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were given numbers on our costumes, uniforms, and again, we were severely beaten and hunger.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They used to call us out, 4:00 in the morning, 5:00 in the morning, for the roll call, and if somebody didn't do something just right or walked away, or-- they would give them whippings, like 25, 30, until they fell unconscious.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, this is Stutthof.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that was the boat ride.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We rode that boat for days, and then we went on-- it was in a ship.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then we rode small boats to get to a train.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then we rode the train for the longest time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I can't even remember how long it was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Days, maybe, yes, and then finally we arrived to Stutthof.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was like hell, itself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As I call it in my compositions, which I will play later, the tunnel of death.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's what I called it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right, there we knew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Stutthof had-- I saw, the chimneys.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right, we knew that there was a crematorium there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was never conscious of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
